---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Button from "./Button.astro";
import hero_image from "../../public/try.jpeg";
---

<div class="relative bg-white py-16">
  <div
    class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 hidden h-1/2 bg-gray-50 lg:block"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
  </div>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl bg-gray-100 lg:bg-transparent lg:px-8">
    <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12">
      <div
        class="relative z-10 lg:col-span-4 lg:col-start-1 lg:row-start-1 lg:bg-transparent lg:py-16"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute inset-x-0 h-1/2 bg-gray-50 lg:hidden"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-md px-6 sm:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-none lg:p-0">
          <div
            class="aspect-h-6 aspect-w-10 sm:aspect-h-1 sm:aspect-w-2 lg:aspect-w-1"
          >
            <Image
              class="rounded-3xl object-cover object-center shadow-2xl"
              src={hero_image}
              alt=""
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="relative bg-[#F2C1D1] lg:col-span-10 lg:col-start-3 lg:row-start-1 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-10 lg:items-center lg:rounded-3xl"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 hidden overflow-hidden rounded-3xl lg:block"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <svg
            class="absolute bottom-full left-full -translate-x-2/3 translate-y-1/3 transform xl:bottom-auto xl:top-0 xl:translate-y-0"
            width="404"
            height="384"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 404 384"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <defs>
              <pattern
                id="64e643ad-2176-4f86-b3d7-f2c5da3b6a6d"
                x="0"
                y="0"
                width="20"
                height="20"
                patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
              >
                <rect
                  x="0"
                  y="0"
                  width="4"
                  height="4"
                  class="text-gray-400"
                  fill="currentColor"
                ></rect>
              </pattern>
            </defs>
            <rect
              width="404"
              height="384"
              fill="url(#64e643ad-2176-4f86-b3d7-f2c5da3b6a6d)"
            ></rect>
          </svg>
          <svg
            class="absolute top-full -translate-x-1/3 -translate-y-1/3 transform xl:-translate-y-1/2"
            width="404"
            height="384"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 404 384"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <defs>
              <pattern
                id="64e643ad-2176-4f86-b3d7-f2c5da3b6a6d"
                x="0"
                y="0"
                width="20"
                height="20"
                patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
              >
                <rect
                  x="0"
                  y="0"
                  width="4"
                  height="4"
                  class="text-[#DE6FA1]"
                  fill="currentColor"
                ></rect>
              </pattern>
            </defs>
            <rect
              width="404"
              height="384"
              fill="url(#64e643ad-2176-4f86-b3d7-f2c5da3b6a6d)"
            ></rect>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div
          class="relative mx-auto max-w-md space-y-6 px-6 py-12 sm:max-w-3xl sm:py-16 lg:col-span-6 lg:col-start-4 lg:max-w-none lg:p-0"
        >
          <h2
            class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900"
            id="join-heading"
          >
            Cum devii mentor?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-base text-zinc-900">
            Mai ții minte cum au fost primii pași în programare? Sau cât de
            curios și motivat erai să descoperi cât mai multe? Înseamnă că
            înțelegi perfect ce caută micii programatori și cum să le stârnești
            interesul. Dacă ești membru AI3 sau ai participat anterior la
            CoderDojo, devino mentor voluntar în echipa noastră.
          </p>
          <Button
            href="mailto:salut+coderdojo@ai3.ro"
            text="Aplică acum"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
